reviewText: I am not sure when my 3 year old and 6 year old grandsons saw their first Tom and Jerry cartoon but they have been hooked ever since.  Personally I have liked some of the earlier ones better than these but not my grandsons.  My youngest grandson is scared by a couple of them but they just go to the menu where they can select their favorites and they watch those over and over.
